high_descs: Turn left, cross the room and go to the cabinet above the toilet
Open the left-hand door of the cabinet and remove the pink spray bottle.
Turn left to face the tub, then turn around and cross the room to face the toilet.
Place the bottle on the toilet tank.
Turn right so the cabinet is on your left.
Open the right-hand cabinet door and remove the pink spray bottle from the cabinet.
Turn right to face the tub , then turn around and cross the room to face the toilet.
Place the bottle on the toilet tank to the right of the other bottle.
anns.task_desc: Take two spray bottles from a cabinet, put them on the toilet tank.

high_descs: Turn left and walk to the to the left cabinet above the toilet.
Pick up the purple spray bottle from the left cabinet.
Walk in front of the toilet.
Place the spray bottle on top of the back of the toilet.
Walk to the right cabinet above the toilet.
Pick up the purple spray bottle from the right cabinet.
Walk to the front of the toilet.
Place the purple spray bottle on top of the back of the toilet.
anns.task_desc: Place two purple spray bottles on top of the back of the toilet.

high_descs: Turn left and turn left again to face the towel.
Open the cabinet to the top right and remove the spray bottle inside, then close the cabinet.
Step back towards the tub, then turn towards the toilet.
Place the spray bottle on top of the toilet.
Turn right towards the wall and open the cabinet to the left.
Take out the spray bottle that is in the cabinet.
Take a step back towards the tub then turn towards the toilet.
Place the spray bottle you're holding to the right of the other spray bottle on top of the toilet.
anns.task_desc: Put two spray bottles on top of the toilet.

high_descs: Turn left, go straight, turn left to face the blue bin next to the toilet, look up.
Take the purple spray bottle from the cabinet above the toilet.
Go backwards while facing towards the blue bin.
Put the spray bottle on the left side of the toilet tank.
Go forward to the blue bin, turn right, look up.
Take the purple spray bottle from the cabinet above that is first from the right.
Turn to face the blue bin. Go backwards while facing towards the blue bin.
Put the spray bottle on the center of the toilet tank.
anns.task_desc: Put two spray bottles on a toilet tank.
